      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>The papers consist chiefly of financial documents regarding
         banking accounts, securities and stock holdings of Barrett,
         his wife, and sons. Most are personal although a few involve
         Barrett's steamship lines. The collection also contains family
         photographs including one of Barrett at an English Speaking
         Union luncheon, an address book, and a movie of the dedication
         of the Barrett Room in Alderman Library.</p>
      </scopecontent>
